## 3. The Momentum Preservation Loop

Corey is a baseline human who relies on chaining industrial physics mechanics to achieve hyper-mobility and "fly" through level geometry.

[ L1 Jet Sprint ] --> [ Square Slag Grenade ] --> [ Frictionless Slide ] --> [ Triangle Rocket Jump ] --> [ Circle Grapnel Slingshot ]

1.  **The Trajectory Booster (Rocket Jump):** Firing the Triangle Rocket at adjacent walls or the ground applies a massive radial kinetic impulse, catapulting Corey into the air.
2.  **The Aerial Control (Hover/Grapnel):** At peak height, pressing Cross fires her hover jets to lock her in space for a DPS window, while pressing Circle latches her grapnel to geometry to swing like a pendulum, changing vector angles without losing speed.
3.  **The DIY Speedtrack (Slag Slide):** Flicking the Right Stick Up and pressing Square deploys a Slag Grenade. Landing from a high-altitude rocket jump directly into this frictionless chemical pool converts all falling vertical speed into maximum horizontal sliding velocity.

---

## 4. The Right-Stick Elemental Matrix (Square Grenades)

Flicking the right analog stick in a cardinal direction instantly updates the chemical compound inside her recharging Hazmat Grenades without shifting her hand off the movement sticks.

*   Up --> Slag (Frictionless / Velocity): Covers the ground in an industrial lubricant for extended, high-speed slides. Caught enemies slip and take increased impact damage.
*   Down --> Pyro (Combustion / Recoil): Leaves a pool of highly volatile, burning chemicals. Discharging the Shotgun or Rocket into a pyro pool triggers a secondary chain-reaction pressure wave, acting as a massive vertical jump booster.
*   Left --> Cryo (Brittle / Stopping Power): Instantly freezes anomalies in a tight radius. The extreme cold compromises their structural integrity, significantly reducing the mechanical effort required for the Circle Grapnel Winch to rip their armor plates off.
*   Right --> Volt (Stun / Kinetic Tether): Drops a localized electromagnetic field that links nearby anomalies together with arcs of lightning. Activating a Triangle Melee Vault on one linked target routes the rocket blast's staggering shockwave down the entire current.

